<p class="lead">SplitText is a component that splits your text into lines, words, and letters so that you can animate them. <br />It supports auto-resizing for lines and styled content when using HTML inside your text.</p>
<p class="lead">Inspired by GSAP's SplitText plugin and SplitType.</p>
